               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Dǝrsān maḥyäwi “The Life-Giving Homily” (fols. 2ra-85va)
 I-1)
                     Introductory prayer (fol. 2ra-rb)
 I-2) Reading for Monday, Compline
                     (nǝwam) (fols. 2va-14ra)
 I-3) Reading for Tuesday, Matins (manfaqa lelit)
                     (fols.14ra-27va)
 I-4) Reading for Wednesday, Lauds (nagh) (fols.
                     27va-37va)
 I-5) Reading for Thursday, Terce (śalastu säʿat) (fols.
                     37va-52ra)
 I-6) Reading for Friday, Sext (qätr) (fols. 52ra-63ra)
                     I-7) Reading for Saturday, None (täsaʿtu säʿat) (fols. 63ra-74rb)
 I-8)
                     Reading for Sunday, Vespers (śark) (fols. 74rb-85va)
 II) Malkǝʾa madḫane
                     ʿālam “Image of the Saviour of the World” (fols. 85va-91ra)
 
 Additio
                     1.</summary>
