                        <condition key="deficient">Both boards, probably not original, are broken
                           and repaired.
 The Ms. was crudely resewn with several threads.
                           Many fols. are damaged at the edges and centrefolds.
 The text is
                           partly not legible due to faded ink (<locus from="2v" to="3r">2v-3r</locus>, 4v-5r, 6v-7r etc.).
 Many fols. are detached from
                           their counterparts.
 f. 1 consists of two unruled pieces of parchment
                           sewn together with parchment strips. 
 Holes or tears amended on
                              <locus target="#52">52</locus> and 57.</condition>
